Uchis、Mannequin Pussy 等</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/english-teacher-bill-ryder-jones-and-beyonce-are-2024s-best-rated-albums-so-far-according-to-metacritic-3752526">据 Metacritic 称，《English Teacher》、《Bill Ryder-Jones》和《Beyoncé》是 2024 年迄今为止评分最高的专辑，它们</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Beyonce-English-Teacher-and-Bill-Ryder-Jones.-Credit-Kevin-Mazur-Lorne-Thomson-and-Richard-Martin-Roberts-via-GETTY.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="碧昂斯、英语老师和比尔·莱德-琼斯。图片来源：Kevin Mazur、Lorne Thomson 和 Richard Martin-Roberts，来自 GETTY" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Beyonce-English-Teacher-and-Bill-Ryder-Jones.-Credit-Kevin-Mazur-Lorne-Thomson-and-Richard-Martin-Roberts-via-GETTY.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Beyonce-English-Teacher-and-Bill-Ryder-Jones.-Credit-Kevin-Mazur-Lorne-Thomson-and-Richard-Martin-Roberts-via-GETTY-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Beyonce-English-Teacher-and-Bill-Ryder-Jones.-Credit-Kevin-Mazur-Lorne-Thomson-and-Richard-Martin-Roberts-via-GETTY-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Beyonce-English-Teacher-and-Bill-Ryder-Jones.-Credit-Kevin-Mazur-Lorne-Thomson-and-Richard-Martin-Roberts-via-GETTY-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Beyonce-English-Teacher-and-Bill-Ryder-Jones.-Credit-Kevin-Mazur-Lorne-Thomson-and-Richard-Martin-Roberts-via-GETTY-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Beyonce-English-Teacher-and-Bill-Ryder-Jones.-Credit-Kevin-Mazur-Lorne-Thomson-and-Richard-Martin-Roberts-via-GETTY-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据<a href="https://www.metacritic.com/browse/albums/score/metascore/year/filtered" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Metacritic</a>称， <a href="/artists/English-Teacher">《English Teacher》</a> 、 <a href="/artists/Bill-Ryder-Jones">《Bill Ryder-Jones》</a>和<a href="/artists/Beyonce">《Beyoncé》</a>已成为 2024 年迄今为止评分最高的专辑。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/english-teacher-this-could-be-texas-debut-album-review-tracklist-radar-3600231">英语老师——“这可能是德克萨斯”评论：一支敢于梦想的乐队</a></strong></li></ul><p>Metacritic 汇总了对电视、电影、书籍和音乐的评论，然后给出平均分。根据他们的<a href="https://www.metacritic.com/about-us/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">“关于我们”页面</a>，该评论聚合网站策划了“一群备受尊敬的评论家，并为他们的评论打分”。然后，他们取“这些分数的加权平均值”，从而得出他们的“元分数”。</p><p>该网站分享了 2024 年迄今为止收视率最高的专辑列表，碧昂斯的乡村专辑《Cowboy Carter》位居榜首。 <em>《NME》</em>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/beyonce-cowboy-carter-album-review-tracklist-lyrics-3611699">对该唱片的五星级评论</a>中写道：“看到[碧昂斯]在一个敢于如此亲密和专注于声音的项目上摇摆如此之大，这是一种不可否认的兴奋。”</p><p> Bill Ryder-Jones 的第五张录音室专辑《Iechyd Da》紧随 Queen Bey 之后，名列榜单第二位。在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/bill-ryder-jones-iechyd-da-review-3568550">对该专辑的五星级评论</a>中， <em>NME</em>分享道：“雄心勃勃、电影感十足、影响力巨大的民谣后续专辑《Iechyd Da》在很多方面都是 Ryder-Jones 自 2013 年以来突破性的专辑《A Bad Wind Blows》所威胁的。在我心里&#39;。” </p><figure id="attachment_3603794" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3603794" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3603794" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Beyonce-Cowboy-Carter-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="碧昂斯《牛仔卡特》专辑封面。图片来源：新闻界" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Beyonce-Cowboy-Carter-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Beyonce-Cowboy-Carter-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Beyonce-Cowboy-Carter-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Beyonce-Cowboy-Carter-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Beyonce-Cowboy-Carter-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Beyonce-Cowboy-Carter-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3603794" class="wp-caption-text">碧昂斯《牛仔卡特》专辑封面。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><p>它继续说道：“他的独奏作品几乎总是非常个人化，这对于这张新的自制唱片来说无疑是正确的：‘iechyd da’是威尔士人对‘身体健康’的祝酒，这张专辑的部分命名是因为他的家族根源国家。它的歌曲与他过去的曲调相呼应，它的声学美学被设置为“渴望”，歌词发现他毫无畏惧地袒露了一切。”</p><p>位居第三的是 English Teacher 及其首张唱片。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/english-teacher-this-could-be-texas-debut-album-review-tracklist-radar-3600231">在对该专辑的五星级评论中</a>， <em>NME</em>分享道：“《This Could Be Texas》中包含了你在首张专辑中想要的一切；从头到尾都是真正原创的作品，声音和文字的冒险，以及具有里程碑意义的声明。准备干大事了吗？谁知道这个行业是否还允许这样做。 </p><figure id="attachment_3614131" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3614131" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3614131" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/english_teacher_nme_andy_ford_2000.jpg" alt="英语老师。图片来源：《NME》安迪·福特" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/english_teacher_nme_andy_ford_2000.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/english_teacher_nme_andy_ford_2000-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/english_teacher_nme_andy_ford_2000-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/english_teacher_nme_andy_ford_2000-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/english_teacher_nme_andy_ford_2000-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/english_teacher_nme_andy_ford_2000-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3614131" class="wp-caption-text">英语老师。图片来源：《NME》安迪·福特</figcaption></figure><p>“不过，这支乐队已经表现出色——他们敢于梦想并获得回报。不是每个人都能去太空，但至少英语老师让被困在这里的该死的地方变得更有趣。”</p><p>紧随其后进入前十名的是 Mannequin Pussy 凭借他们的第四张唱片《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/mannequin-pussy-3593156">I Got Heaven</a> 》排名第四，Waxahatchee 的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/waxahatchee-tigers-blood-review-americana-stalwart-at-the-top-of-her-game-3604347">Tigers Blood</a> 》排名第五，St. Vincent 令人振奋的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/st-vincent-all-born-screaming-review-3749641">All Born Screaming</a> 》排名第六，《Vampire》 Weekend 的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/vampire-weekend-only-god-was-above-us-review-3613120">Only God Was Over Us》</a>排名第七，Brittany Howard 的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/brittany-howard-what-now-review-3584375">What Now</a> 》排名第八，Kali Uchis 的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/kali-uchis-orquideas-review-lyrics-tracklist-3569143">Orquídeas</a> 》排名第九，Riff Raff 的《The Past Is Still Alive》排名第七10号。</p><p>其他消息方面，2019 年《狮子王》前传<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/moonlight-director-barry-jenkins-tapped-to-film-lion-king-sequel-2764623"><em>《木法沙》</em></a>的首支预告片<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/beyonce-donald-glover-lion-king-prequel-mufasa-trailer-3751842"><em>已</em>发布，确认碧昂斯和唐纳德·格洛弗将回归</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/english-teacher-bill-ryder-jones-and-beyonce-are-2024s-best-rated-albums-so-far-according-to-metacritic-3752526">据 Metacritic 称，《English Teacher》、《Bill Ryder-Jones》和《Beyoncé》是 2024 年迄今为止评分最高的专辑，它们</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
